    <summary>Eloquent ORM patterns: $fillable whitelisting, scopes, Attribute::make() accessors, N+1 prevention via eager loading, and DB transactions.</summary>
    <tags>
      <tag>eloquent</tag>
      <tag>laravel</tag>
      <tag>orm</tag>
      <tag>database</tag>
      <tag>performance</tag>
